    %h2 Sports

    %p
      When it comes to sports, were not aiming to make you into the next
      Michael Jordan or Ronaldo: we just want you to have a ton of fun
      playing lacrosse, street hockey, or one of a dozen other sports offered,
      while learning something new about it at the same time. Everybody gets
      to play here, so if you’re looking to learn more about a sport you've
      never played before or if you’re a seasoned pro you will have fun and,
      hopefully learn something new.

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
