  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Street Hockey

    %p
      Take a slap shot, play a scrimmage, practice your passing: at our top-notch
      Street Hockey court, you can do it all. We’ll teach you anything you want to
      know about the fast-paced game of Street Hockey, no matter what your previous skill level;
      so shoot away, you can't miss!

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
    %iframe{ :src => 'http://player.vimeo.com/video/32745011?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0', :width => 456, :height => 324 }

  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Baseball

    %p
      We’ve got two basketball courts to play on; after flag lowering, there's usually
      a huge game of Knockout on the Knoll. We’ll be more than happy to teach you anything
      you want to know, or just jump into a pickup game.

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
    %iframe{ :src => 'http://player.vimeo.com/video/31702778?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0', :width => 456, :height => 324 }

  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Volleyball

    %p
      Never played before? No problem: we'll have you digging and spiking in no time.
      Our sand volleyball courts kept the impact low, and the spirit high—so serve
      it up, we’re always ready to volley.

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
    %iframe{ :src => 'http://player.vimeo.com/video/32744751?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0', :width => 456, :height => 324 }

  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 International Sports

    %p
      Every played Touch Rugby before? How about Cricket? If not, then here's your opportunity.
      Our international staff are ready and waiting to teach you games that we play on this side
      of the pond — you may find you’ve been missing out.

