  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Arena Soccer

    %p
      Our brand new arena soccer court is home to our unique arena soccer program.
      Offered as and instructional class, the focus is to use tight ball handling skills
      and the arena walls themselves to best the other team.

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
    %iframe{ :src => 'http://player.vimeo.com/video/32744962?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0', :width => 456, :height => 324 }

  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Tennis

    %p
      Our tennis courts are a great place to work on your serve, practice volleys at the net,
      or just play a round of King of the Court. We’ve got a brand new wall to practice
      rallying by yourself, and, if you want, we can bring out the Pickleball for a whole different type of game.

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
    %iframe{ :src => 'http://player.vimeo.com/video/31093270?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0', :width => 456, :height => 324 }

  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 LaCrosse

    %p
      Even if you have never touched a stick before, our instructors have the
      experience to get you passing, shooting, and defending in no time at all.
      In just a single afternoon you will have already learned the basics and
      moved on to more important things: having fun!

  .shadow.rounded.video.space
