  .liner.shadow.rounded.space
    %h2 Soccer

    %p
      We're ready to help you learn all about the world’s favorite sport.
      With a round of World Cup or a game against another camp, you'll
      have every chance you want to work on your game. Take a run out
      onto the pitch; we'll be right beside you.

